MAX node at A, alpha=-inf, beta=inf
MIN node at B, alpha=-inf, beta=inf
MAX node at D, alpha=-inf, beta=inf
 MAX visiting child 3, value=3, updated alpha=3
 MAX visiting child 5, value=5, updated alpha=5
 MIN visiting child D, value=5, updated beta=5
