 MAX visiting child 6, value=6, updated alpha=6
  PRUNED remaining children of E (beta=5, alpha=6)
 MIN visiting child E, value=6, updated beta=5
 MAX visiting child B, value=5, updated alpha=5
MIN node at C, alpha=5, beta=inf
MAX node at F, alpha=5, beta=inf
 MAX visiting child 1, value=1, updated alpha=5
 MAX visiting child 2, value=2, updated alpha=5
 MIN visiting child F, value=2, updated beta=2
  PRUNED remaining children of C (beta=2, alpha=5)
 MAX visiting child C, value=2, updated alpha=5

Final Value at Root A = 5
